high_descs: Turn around towards the sink at the back.
Pick up fork from the sink.
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the counter top on your right.
Place fork on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Shifting fork from one place to another.

high_descs: Turn around left to the sink.
Take a fork from the sink.
Turn left, move forward, turn right, move forward, turn right, move forward a while. Turn right, move forward, and turn right to the countertop.
Place a fork on top right corner of the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Place a fork on the countertop from the sink.

high_descs: Pick the fork from the sink.
Place the fork on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: To place the fork on the countertop.
